Config::Terse
==============

Config::Terse is laconic configuration files parser.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Config::Terse requires the following non-core perl modules:

    Carp for error reporting.

